<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
<h1>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</h1>

<% if @languages.count == 1 %>
  <% lang = @languages.first.first %>
  <% last_update = @languages.first.second %>
    <p>You are the primary point person for the <span style="font-size: x-large"><%= lang.name %></span> language in LCI.
    This language hasn't seen any updates for <%= time_ago_in_words(last_update) %>.</p>
  <p>Please log into the <%= link_to 'LCI App', login_url %>
    and go to the <%= link_to "#{lang.name} details page", show_details_language_url(lang.id) %></p>
<% else %>
  <p>You are the primary point person for each of the following languages.
  These particular languages haven't seen an update in a while.</p>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Language</th><th>Last updated</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% @languages.each do |lang, last_updated| %>
        <tr>
          <td style="font-size: x-large"><%= link_to lang.name, show_details_language_url(lang.id) %></td>
          <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= time_ago_in_words(last_updated) %> ago</td>
        </tr>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p>Please log into the <%= link_to 'LCI App', login_url %>
    and go to the details page of each of these languages to check they are up to date.</p>
<% end %>
<p>If you find any information that needs to be changed you may make an edit on the language details page.</p>
<p>This email was automatically generated from the LCI App.
  If you feel you should not have received it please contact your LCI supervisor or replay to this email.</p>
</body>
</html>